trans-unit.source: Represents an <xref:System.Int32> property (and the value of the property) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en <xref:System.Int32>egenskap (och värdet för egenskapen) av en utskrift maskinvaru- eller systemkomponent.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> klass för den angivna egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Int32> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Den `attributeName` ska skrivas exakt samma som namnet på en viss <xref:System.Int32>-egenskapen för ett utskriftssystem objekt, inklusive versaler och gemener.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "AveragePagesPerMinute", not "AveragePPM" or "AveragePagesperMinute".
trans-unit.target: Till exempel den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>egenskapen för en <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objekt måste skrivas "AveragePagesPerMinute", inte "AveragePPM" eller "AveragePagesperMinute".</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref:System.Int32> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Namnet på den <xref:System.Int32>egenskapen som den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> representerar.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> class for the specified attribute and gives it the specified value.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> klass för det angivna attributet och ger det angivna värdet.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Int32> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: Den `attributeName` ska skrivas exakt samma som namnet på en viss <xref:System.Int32>-egenskapen för ett utskriftssystem objekt, inklusive versaler och gemener.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "AveragePagesPerMinute", not "AveragePPM" or "AveragePagesperMinute".
trans-unit.target: Till exempel den <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>egenskapen för en <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>objekt måste skrivas "AveragePagesPerMinute", inte "AveragePPM" eller "AveragePagesperMinute".</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name of the <xref:System.Int32> property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Namnet på den <xref:System.Int32>egenskapen som den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> representerar.</xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: The value of <xref:System.Object> the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> represents.
Gets or sets the value of the property that the <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"></xref> represents.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger värdet på egenskapen som den <xref href="System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property"> </xref> representerar.

trans-unit.source: The property cannot be set to the value that the calling code provides.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen kan inte anges till det värde som den anropande koden.
